  "response": "Here are some unconventional ways to enjoy French fries:\n\n1. Unique Toppings\n- Kimchi fries\n- Truffle oil and parmesan\n- Curry sauce\n- Chili and cheese\n- Poutine (gravy and cheese curds)\n\n2. Global Fusion\n- Mexican-style with salsa and guacamole\n- Greek-style with feta and tzatziki\n- Korean BBQ-style with gochujang\n- Mediterranean with hummus\n\n3. Breakfast-Style\n- Top with fried egg\n- Add bacon bits\n- Include scrambled eggs\n- Serve with hollandaise sauce\n\n4. Dessert-Inspired\n- Cinnamon sugar fries\n- Chocolate drizzle\n- Nutella and powdered sugar\n- Caramel sauce\n\n5. Unusual Preparations\n- Waffle fries\n- Spiral-cut fries\n- Loaded potato skins\n- Fry nachos\n- Fry grilled cheese sandwich\n\n6. Serving Styles\n- In a cone\n- Served in a paper bag\n- As a base for other dishes\n- Wrapped in a tortilla\n\nThese options offer creative ways to elevate the classic French fry experience.",
